Operon BPM-Trendy 16 Wrist Bp Monitor Price: Rs.1300

Key Features

  • Easy Self-testing Device

With the Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor you could now measure your blood pressure at the privacy of your own home and be able to obtain the same level of accuracy that hospital professionals depend on.  Using a simple yet advanced operating technology this blood pressure detector allows Easy Self-Testing.


The home monitoring facility of this blood pressure monitor helps you keep a constant check on your blood pressure level and alerts you and your doctors to possible health complications. In addition to this the device also offers Irregular Heart Beat Detection notifying you of your health condition and helping you prevent serious health problems.


Build


This modern blood pressure monitor from Operon comes with a huge LCD display giving you a better view of your heart beat and blood pressure readings.  Furthermore this clear digital display shows the date and time of your readings. The trendily designed blood pressure monitor has a flexible wrist cuff and its circumference ranges from 12.5 x 21 cm.


This compact Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor comprising of WHO indicator weighs 120g making it an easily portable device and has dimensions of 67.7mm x 87.4 mm x 32.3 mm (WXHXD).  Monitoring your blood pressure with this wrist type blood pressure monitor involves a quick three step process.


All you need to do is simply wrap the cuff around our wrist and make sure the cuff is placed in the right manner.  You could then turn on the start button on the control panel. The cuff will automatically inflate at the touch of the start button reading your heart rate and checking your blood pressure.


Performance


The Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist Bp Monitor has an in-built inflation detection function which allows instant inflation of the cuff to an optimal level providing you quick and precise readings. The blood pressure readings of this wrist type monitor are equal to Auscultation- cuff/stethescope method and hence capable of giving you accurate and consistent measurements.

Enabling a 2 user facility this digitalized blood pressure monitor is bestowed with a 90 readings memory and capable of providing an average measurement of the last 3 readings. This helps you keep  a continuous track on the progression in your blood and heart rate levels. Apart from this Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor is also embedded with a 3 Set Alarm Setting thereby providing remarkable operating performance.


Adding to the comfort this smart blood pressure monitor has a Low Battery Indicator which saves power and increases battery life. This digital Operon BPM-16 Trendy Wrist BP Monitor displays readings ranging from 30 to 280 mmHg for pressure readings and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse rates. The accuracy rate of the BP monitor is regulated at +/-3 mmHg for pressure reading and +/-4% of reading for pulse progress.  This trendy device is powered by 2 x 1.5V AAA Alkaline batteries.

Operon Comfort 623 Arm Type Bp Monitor Price: Rs.1400

Key Features

  • Single Button Operation

Managing your blood pressure level is now made simpler and easier with the Operon BPM-623 Comfort Upper Arm Bp Monitor. It is important that persons with high blood pressure keep an acute check on their varying pressure levels. This clinically proven arm -type blood pressure monitor helps you accomplish this concern. Designed with a WHO indicator this user-friendly blood pressure monitor helps you generate blood pressure and pulse readings simultaneously with just a click of a button.


Build


Equipped with a jumbo LCD screen the Operon BPM-623 Comfort Upper Arm Bp Monitor facilitates easy viewing and improved readability. This blood pressure monitor comes with an easy -to- wrap medium arm flexible cuff and its circumference ranges from 23 – 33 cm. Understanding your health related requirements the operation of this blood pressure monitor is made smarter and simpler.


You could measure your blood pressure and pulse readings in a quick three step procedure. Position yourself comfortably on a chair with your feet firm on the ground. Ensure that your arm rests on the table so that the sleeve is at the same level as your heart and place the flexible cuff around your arm. On the push of the start button the cuff inflates and deflates giving you precise and quick readings. 


Performance


The Operon BPM-623 Comfort Upper Arm Bp Monitor uses the Oscillometric Method to read the level of blood pressure and pulse. This Oscillometric method operates by identifying the magnitude of oscillations caused by the blood as it begins to flow again into the limb. The readings acquired from this blood pressure monitor are accurate and comparable to Cuff and Stethescope method of generating blood pressure readings.


The memory feature of this blood pressure monitor from Operon is capable of storing 60 readings helping you check the progress in your blood pressure level. This upper arm blood pressure observer displays readings ranging from 30 mmHg to 280 mmHg for pressure and 40 to 199 beats/minute for pulse. The accuracy of this monitor is calibrated at a rate of +/-3 mmHg for pressure readings and +/-4% of reading for pulse progress.


The convenient operating temperature of this device ranges from 10 degree Celsius – 40 degree Celsius with relative humidity up to 85%. The appropriate storing temperature of this device ranges from -20 degree Celsius to 50 degree Celsius. Crafted with a low battery indicator this blood pressure monitor cautions you when the device is running short on power. This Operon BPM-623 Comfort Upper Arm Bp Monitor is powered by 4 x 1.5V AA size alkaline batteries. Weighing 260 g this Bp monitor is easily portable.
